amendatorysection.catchline: Dentist and Dental Hygienist Compact; compact privilege to practice.
amendatorysection.para: A person holding a compact privilege to practice in Nebraska under the Dentist and Dental Hygienist Compact may engage in the practice of dentistry or dental hygiene as authorized pursuant to such compact.

crossreference.para: Dentist and Dental Hygienist Compact, see section 38-4801.
